==English==

===Etymology===

From [[Latin]] ''[[-abilitas]]''; forming nouns from adjectives ending in ''[[-abilis]]''. Not etymologically related to '''[[ability]]'''.

===Suffix===
'''-ability'''
# Ability, [[inclination]] or [[suitability]] for a [[specified]] [[function]] or [[condition]].

